g.text: 7Phone microphone records speech of SGuardianwhich is sent to our backend Node-RED server.Node-RED server calls Watson Speech to Text Service to use machine learning to translate user speech.Node-RED server receives transcript and passes it to Watson Assistant service.

Watson Assistant, finetuned with SCDF guidelines on how to perform first aid, uses natural language understanding to formulate the best response to guide the SGuardian.Watson Assistant's response is sent to Watson Text to Speech.Watson Text to Speech encodes the message in the user's language.Node-RED server sends the verbal response back to the SGuardapp.
